mere
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a short flat bone, stone or greenstone hand-club. [Maori] ;  mere ... n. Maori war-club [Maori]; a short flat weapon of stone for hand-to-hand fighting (Williams) Maori,<i> mere</i> (occas. <i>meremere</i>)


